                <text type="forecast">Partly cloudy. Very high chance of showers, most likely in the afternoon and evening. Winds northerly 15 to 20 km/h turning westerly 25 to 35 km/h in the middle of the day. Overnight temperatures falling to around 8 with daytime temperatures reaching around 18.</text>
