                <text type="forecast">Partly cloudy. Medium chance of showers, most likely in the afternoon. Winds northwesterly 15 to 25 km/h tending westerly 20 to 30 km/h during the day then becoming light during the evening. Overnight temperatures falling to around 8 with daytime temperatures reaching around 17.</text>
